---

## Acceptance Summary

- Login and signup now use native Swift hashing.
- Active sign-in/sign-up request signing now uses native Swift HMAC.
- Device-id ciphertext path uses native Swift AES.
- Backend compatibility validated in testing after Keccak parity fix.
- No active runtime path requires JavaScriptCore-based crypto execution.

